            candidate at an election held under <ref>section 6</ref> of the Chief Executive Election
            Ordinance (<ref href="/hk/cap569">Cap. 569</ref>) is—
            <sourceNote>(<ref href="/hk/2016/ln34">L.N. 34 of
                2016</ref>)</sourceNote></leadIn><paragraph name="a" id="ID_1457426685179_001" temporalId="s2_a"><num value="a">(a)</num><content>if the date of the poll at the election is before
                27
                March 2022—$15,700,000; or</content></paragraph><paragraph name="b" id="ID_1457426685179_002" temporalId="s2_b"><num value="b">(b)</num><content>if the date of the poll at the election is on or after
                27
                March 2022—$17,600,000.</content></paragraph><sourceNote>(<ref href="/hk/2011/18">18 of 2011 s. 42</ref>; <ref href="/hk/2016/ln34">L.N.
                34 of
            2016</ref>; <ref href="hk/2021/14">14 of 2021 s. 380</ref>)</sourceNote></section></main></subLeg>